{"tid":810140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北海道地震停電証明日本絕對唔能夠全面電子貨幣化化","createTime":"2018-09-07T16:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T20:49:39.000Z","uid":22675,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7644fa2e9b3ca12d2e402f34607884953278a469","tid":810140,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T16:53:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/08/005306_60d948510a2d47fbcd97c5592f5b3428.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F08%2F005306_60d948510a2d47fbcd97c5592f5b3428.png&h=a0023f7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北海道停電，用不了電子貨幣<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.japhub.com/201809/IgVlprBt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F201809%2FIgVlprBt.jpg&h=83a4deab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北海道發電站因地震造成損毀，整個北海道停電，需要一星期以上才能完全復修發電站的電力運作。許多便利店和超級市場在停電的狀況下照常營業，讓災民購買食品和日常用品。不過，習慣使用電子貨幣的災民，卻是有錢也買不到物資。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n事源，一位北海道災民在匿名留言版上發文，講述自己處於極度糟糕的狀況。由於電子貨幣太方便，他平日基本上只用Apple Pay付款。最近甚至不帶銀包，身上近乎沒有現金。在9月6日凌晨3時，他感受到地震，接著就是餘震和停電。受驚的他打開雪櫃，發現只有牛奶和蛋黃醬。於是，急忙的走到便利店買物資。到達便利店時才發現，自己身上沒有現金，只有剩下62%電力的iPhone。他看著電話上Apple Pay的畫面，只能感到絕望。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n除了這位災民，亦有不少災民在推特表示處於同一處境，身上沒有現金購買糧食。據說，部份7-11便利店有緊急電源，可以使用電子貨幣。不過，這次北海道停電引起網民熱議「日本不可能電子貨幣完全取代現金」。因為日本經常發生地震，隨之而來的停電會導致無法使用電子貨幣，所以現金還是不可取代的。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.japhub.com/201809/lhUeLmK1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F201809%2FlhUeLmK1.jpg&h=771ac57b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼ 據經濟產業省於2015年的調查，日本國民使用電子貨幣結帳的比率較其他先進國低。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.japhub.com/201809/gCDBtfnD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.japhub.com%2F201809%2FgCDBtfnD.jpg&h=6815642e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de5a6c289517f737dca808fc5b783b5fe53b2c68","tid":810140,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T16:53:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://japhub.com/?c=8094\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjaphub.com%2F%3Fc%3D8094&d=jscOkhO2TpumRN1fB%2Fr55MVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=a8e7215e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://japhub.com/?c=8094</a>"},{"pid":"1b092b8c384dd0e1a0af6894158001c07ec3acc0","tid":810140,"uid":155818,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T16:56:27.000Z","msg":"跟本就反智全面電子化<br />\n任何野一過量就適得其反<br />\n又唔見歐洲嗰邊玩&gt;?<br />\n大陸仔剩係識得吹"},{"pid":"25748d7a37c14e4f332ecf7bee54cf8711118e02","tid":810140,"uid":77320,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T16:56:33.000Z","msg":"另大邊廂<br />\n香港正引入FPS<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b2fa450822faf3acdd42670f94c2f3177c9caa","tid":810140,"uid":77320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T16:56:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另一邊廂<br />\n香港正引入FPS<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a8c897ccd80f7babd1a817234119ceaaacdbd8c8","tid":810140,"uid":77320,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1b092b8c384dd0e1a0af6894158001c07ec3acc0","tid":810140,"uid":155818,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T16:56:27.000Z","msg":"跟本就反智全面電子化<br />\n任何野一過量就適得其反<br />\n又唔見歐洲嗰邊玩&gt;?<br />\n大陸仔剩係識得吹"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T16:57:26.000Z","msg":"大陸有trust issue<br />\n假銀紙"},{"pid":"fcdf098841edda68be3478bb7714bfa79b2e701b","tid":810140,"uid":43061,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T16:59:51.000Z","msg":"支那有天災仲同你比錢咩<br />\n入鋪頭搶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a6245e28583deaed9a8d29b5dd4501ef676205d","tid":810140,"uid":1821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T17:02:56.000Z","msg":"豪州即係邊度？"},{"pid":"f4406a7679dc868ff10dadcb9828d9e59097b4ab","tid":810140,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a6245e28583deaed9a